  03 May 2012; Jeff Horelick <jdhore@gentoo.org> razertool-0.0.7-r3.ebuild:
  dev-util/pkgconfig -> virtual/pkgconfig

  28 Mar 2011; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  razertool-0.0.7-r3.ebuild:
  Install 90-razertool.rules to /lib/udev instead of /etc/udev.

  23 Mar 2011; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  razertool-0.0.7-r3.ebuild:
  Use SLOT dependencies for x11-libs/gtk+.

*razertool-0.0.7-r3 (07 Apr 2010)

  07 Apr 2010; Bernard Cafarelli <voyageur@gentoo.org>
  -razertool-0.0.7-r2.ebuild, +razertool-0.0.7-r3.ebuild:
  plugdev is created by hal, use usb group by default instead

*razertool-0.0.7-r2 (06 Apr 2010)

  06 Apr 2010; Bernard Cafarelli <voyageur@gentoo.org>
  -razertool-0.0.7-r1.ebuild, +razertool-0.0.7-r2.ebuild:
  HAL is dead, bug #313393

*razertool-0.0.7-r1 (07 Dec 2009)

  07 Dec 2009; Bernard Cafarelli <voyageur@gentoo.org>
  -razertool-0.0.7.ebuild, +razertool-0.0.7-r1.ebuild:
