  switch to EAPI 2

  16 May 2009; Robin H. Johnson <robbat2@gentoo.org> razertool-0.0.7.ebuild:
  Migration to virtual/libusb. Verified by testing hardware (by
  Polynomial-C).

  05 Oct 2008; Thomas Anderson <gentoofan23@gentoo.org>
  razertool-0.0.7.ebuild:
  Add missing pkconfig dependency, bug #239614

  28 Aug 2008; Bernard Cafarelli <voyageur@gentoo.org>
  razertool-0.0.7.ebuild:
  Add warning on older firmwares, icon and desktop entry. Thanks Lars
  <polynomial-C@gmx.de> in bug #235946

